V
V
 \left\{ \begin{array}{ll} V = 0 & \text{ if } X < \frac{1}{6} \\ V = 1 & \text{ if } \frac{1}{6} \leq X < \frac{3}{6} \\ V = 2 & \text{ if } X \geq \frac{3}{6} \end{array} \right. 
 f_{V}\left(v\right) = \left\{ \begin{array}{ll} \frac{1}{6} & \text{ if } v = 0 \\ \frac{2}{6} & \text{ if } v = 1 \\ \frac{1}{2} & \text{ if } v = 2 \end{array} \right. 
V
 f_{V}\left(v\right) = \frac{\mathrm d}{\mathrm dx}F_{V}(v) 
